{"tid":1360110,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（公務員請入）見到咁多同路公僕，會唔會搵個工會統籌罷工？","createTime":"2019-07-24T09:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T00:32:24.000Z","uid":134834,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d1708e59002e26e67177ce975fbf16bc0b350fe8","tid":1360110,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:33:26.000Z","msg":"眼見咁多同路人，同埋有明文規定公務員可以罷工，<br />\n會唔會搵職工盟考慮下罷工既可能性？<br />\n有工會帶頭會好好多，拋磚引玉，<br />\n希望各路人馬提出意見"},{"pid":"eb1a71454563e762739579eaa7422499292b5ba9","tid":1360110,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"自隊三post"},{"pid":"c511246072b98f101dafe1617bfc049b1a31caa4","tid":1360110,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"第二隊！"},{"pid":"73ad29b288e48cbb9bd64fe69627573c7851b883","tid":1360110,"uid":134834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"第三隊！"},{"pid":"1a27a1a91102e1930b00275800113abc99f9f92e","tid":1360110,"uid":47798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"罷工一定會有老鬼或鞋精唔會跟<br />\n<br />\n但各位可以病假<br />\n幾百蚊攞兩日病假<br />\n<br />\n多人病假唔夠人手<br />\n啲老鬼同鞋精要做埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點係你病假病假紙<br />\n符合遊戲規則佢咬你唔食<br />\n<br />\n最多無得升最多appraisal唔靚"},{"pid":"99c724c8e36a9fd98ef89ff8db0fc21085d86fd1","tid":1360110,"uid":197570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:16:43.000Z","msg":"揾咗，但暫未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n但如果無工會撐，我地仲有咩方法可以號召公務員唔驚被炒響應罷工？"},{"pid":"926548cc600abf4fc10149f08e6493a6368e15df","tid":1360110,"uid":27605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:43:08.000Z","msg":"工會個個撐警架<br />\n個個舊制老屎忽<br />\n表得態既8-9成都係新制"},{"pid":"aff04149e8d4577ce84eea199ae5b7d4bce4c1ae","tid":1360110,"uid":243407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:46:23.000Z","msg"